Additional bundled dependencies
--------------------------------

This software statically links the following system libraries, which are
included in the binary wheels:

- expat: XML parser library (MIT License)
  Used by fontconfig for parsing XML configuration files.
  https://libexpat.github.io/

- zlib: Compression library (zlib License)
  Used by freetype and fontconfig for data compression.
  https://www.zlib.net/

Note: When building from source, these libraries are linked during the build
process and may need to be installed via system package managers.
